org.apache.freemarker.core.model.impl

Class SimpleJavaMethodModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.freemarker.core.model.impl.SimpleJavaMethodModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.freemarker.core._UnexpectedTypeErrorExplainerTemplateModel, JavaMethodModel, TemplateCallableModel, TemplateFunctionModel, TemplateModel, TemplateModelWithOriginName

    public final class SimpleJavaMethodModel
extends Object
implements JavaMethodModel, org.apache.freemarker.core._UnexpectedTypeErrorExplainerTemplateModel
    Wraps a Method into the TemplateFunctionModel interface. It is used by BeanModel to wrap non-overloaded methods.
    See Also:
    OverloadedJavaMethodModel
